# GitHub Action ships only its bundled entry point in-tree (checked out by
# `uses: jaydrao215/deslint/action@main`). Ignore compiler sidecars and
# per-file TS output that can appear from IDE/tsc runs.
!action/dist/
action/dist/*
!action/dist/index.js

